message.body: There's a Peruvian/Portuguese restaurant that i have heard good things about in north east Philly. We should check it out Thursday night.
Yuuuummmm. But, alas, I will be on my way to Firefly Festival :)
Also, Jo says she figured out who you reminded her of. Chris Evans
I am pretty sure they make food on days other than Thursdays. Do you want to go another time, like tomorrow or next week?
I looked up Chris Evans in that there internet and was pleasantly surprised when i saw my supposed doppelganger.
